    \<Longrightarrow> notime.htriple ba.\<alpha> (ba.pto xx (p +\<^sub>a i)) (checked_idx_ptr p i) (\<lambda>r. \<up>(r=p +\<^sub>a i) ** ba.pto xx (p +\<^sub>a i))"
